text: Noël Soetaert (born 23 November 1949) is a former Belgian cyclist. He competed in the tandem event at the 1972 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1949 births Category:Living people Category:Belgian male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of Belgium Category:Cyclists at the 1972 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from West Flanders Category:People from Middelkerke
